				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For the politician, see <a href="Fiona_Bruce_(politician)" title="Fiona Bruce (politician)">Fiona Bruce (politician)</a>.</div>
